title: Carnival Eats S01E03 Oak Mountain Rattlesnake Festival WEB-DL.x2
description:
Carnival Eats - Season 1, Episode 3




Oak Mountain Spring State Fair/Apache Rattlesnake Festival

On this episode, host Noah Cappe travels to Oklahoma for the Apache Rattlesnake Festival. He bravely samples the Deep Fried Rattlesnake, the namesake dish of the festival. Later, Noah takes in the treats at Alabama's Oak Mountain Spring Fair.




Original Air Date: 01-Sep-2014
